snippet.title: Amber Heard Takes A Moment For Fans At Pre-Golden Globes Party
snippet.description:
Saturday, January 7, 2017 - Amber Heard dazzles in a shimmering gold dress at the pre-Golden Globes Art of Elysium Gala honoring Stevie Wonder's "HEAVEN."
